How's he supposed to get that off you if you keep moving?

269
00:12:24,399 --> 00:12:31,759
Guys, I can hear, this seems crazy, but I can hear the dagger in my head,

270
00:12:31,759 --> 00:12:34,319
and it's saying something bad is going to happen to one of you

271
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:36,879
if it's separated from me.

272
00:12:38,639 --> 00:12:42,159
I mean, it already used you to stab Thaddeus.

273
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,439
What worse could happen to us?

274
00:12:44,879 --> 00:12:47,759
That seems like a risky fucking thing to ask.

275
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:48,879
What worse could happen?

276
00:12:48,879 --> 00:12:52,159
We've just been in a death maze for like nine and a half months.

277
00:12:53,039 --> 00:12:54,000
Fair point, fair point.

278
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:54,480
It's noted.

279
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:58,959
Nularaa, you hear the voice come back and it says,

280
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:03,519
yes, yes, he was weak, but he looks fine now.

