00:13:04,319 --> 00:13:08,639
Guys, this dagger is evil.

282
00:13:08,639 --> 00:13:11,679
It's so evil, it's happy that I stabbed Thaddeus.

283
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,680
Of course it made me stab him.

284
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:15,600
I didn't think it would regret it now, but.

285
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,400
It really takes it back down.

286
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,360
It's like, oh, you know what?

287
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,080
It should have done that.

288
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,120
It was a step too far.

289
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:25,040
But Nularaa, if we don't try to separate you from it,

290
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,240
you might just end up stabbing one of us again.

291
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:32,480
But if we do try to separate you from it, something bad's going to happen.

292
00:13:34,160 --> 00:13:34,720
I guess.

293
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:38,000
This is like the epitome of rock in a hard place, isn't it?

294
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,080
What does it want?

295
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:44,160
I don't know.

296
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,880
Dagger, what do you want?

297
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:51,360
I roll my wolf eyes at her.

298
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:54,960
I roll my wolfy eyes at her like, you give me this attitude now.

299
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:59,040
What I want will become clear soon.

