310
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:29,600
Fucking help me.

311
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:31,920
Guys, help me.

312
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:33,920
Make me not do anything bad again.

313
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:35,440
I don't want this to happen again.

314
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,480
Can we tie our hands together?

315
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:42,080
You hear in your head, Nularaa.

316
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:46,560
If you don't try to get rid of me, I won't make you hurt your friends again.

